{"tid":1642971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【預咗比人鬧分化】和理非Freeriders死全家","createTime":"2019-10-10T02:37:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T17:31:06.000Z","uid":221035,"like":24,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6b63396f2067a97348db43e96c60b15cf9458c3e","tid":1642971,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T02:37:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和理非冇問題，但和理非得嚟仲要freeride就真係死全家<br />\n又話裝修太暴力，變咗黑裝修、紅裝飾。而家呢？裝飾咗啲咩呀？<br />\n蒙面法你話好嬲好嬲，口罩都唔敢戴係想點？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拒絕Freeride</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">淨係想大家應承我一樣嘢：無論如何都不做freerider</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">1 聽晚18區 2100 和你開花</span></strong>：唔好淨係唱歌，既然call得人落黎，順便<strong>修復連儂牆，一齊貼文宣</strong>，仲有嫌裝修暴力嘅，<strong>唔該趁聽日真係「紅裝飾」</strong>，你再唔裝飾得個講字，遲啲被人裝修，你就無資格批評<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">2 星期六 1300 黨鐵商場和你shop</span></strong>：想大家升級，如果夠人，<strong>全部坐晒係商場唔同出入口，逼佢閂門收皮</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">3 每日返放工／學 全民口罩</span></strong>：<strong>講過好多次，如果唔係身處集會／遊行／非法集結，自己戴口罩係完全合法，唔好再講咩流感，呢個係你嘅個人表態，戴口罩就係反極權抗惡法，唔好搵其他藉口咁肉酸</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>唔好係連登講咗當做咗得唔得？</strong><br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n如果未睇就快啲睇，keep住問自己點樣可以做多啲，唔好freeride<br />\n<br />\n[極高質] 香港家書：黎明不會從天而降<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ajAbbQU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ajAbbQU</a>"},{"pid":"06975583da731fab3b93832777d3c5ed4945fa15","tid":1642971,"uid":221035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T02:37:39.000Z","msg":"Freeriders死全家"},{"pid":"e1a6968460ed1ce48c63b2913e2764955cb6c427","tid":1642971,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T02:37:49.000Z","msg":"Freeriders死全家"},{"pid":"702e99654d353ab0ee802b57a342c8cdaca160ab","tid":1642971,"uid